data.description: A place to call home! Conveniently located in the quiet and friendly neighborhood of the Flower Tract, this 3BR / 2BA home is boasting with opportunity.  Azelea is only two blocks, ending in a cul-de-sac, making traffic sparse and parking plentiful.  You’ll enjoy great restaurants, Knotts Berry Farm, shopping and immediate access to the 91 freeway.  With a large, private pool out back and peaceful walking streets in front, your “no place like home” offers something for everyone and every pet!
